actions.code:
function run(data) {
  console.log('storing shopify cart', data)
  const cartData = data.cartCreate ?? data.cartLinesAdd ?? data.cartLinesUpdate ?? data
  const shopifyCart = {
    id: cartData.cart.id,
    checkoutUrl: cartData.cart.checkoutUrl,
    totalPrice: cartData.cart.cost.totalAmount.amount,
    subtotalPrice: cartData.cart.cost.subtotalAmount.amount,
    totalTaxPrice: cartData.cart.cost.totalTaxAmount.amount,
    products: cartData.cart.lines.edges.map(edge => ({
      cartLineId: edge.node.id,
      quantity: edge.node.quantity,
      merchandiseId: edge.node.merchandise.id,
      name: edge.node.merchandise.product.title,
      imageUrl: edge.node.merchandise.product.featuredImage?.url,
      price: edge.node.merchandise.price.amount,
    }))
  }
  console.log('shopifyCart', shopifyCart)
  state.shopifyCart = shopifyCart
  actions.setCookie('cartId', shopifyCart.id)
}
